ext-brand-700 font-medium text-slate-700\">Shop for<svg class=\"h-3 w-3 transition-transform \" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M19 9l-7 7-7-7\"></path></svg></button></div><a class=\"text-sm transition hover:text-brand-700 font-medium text-slate-700\" href=\"/compare\">Compare</a><a class=\"text-sm transition hover:text-brand-700 font-medium text-slate-700\" href=\"/questions\">Questions?</a><a class=\"text-sm transition hover:text-brand-700 font-medium text-slate-700\" href=\"/about\">About</a><a aria-current=\"page\" class=\"text-sm transition hover:text-brand-700 font-semibold text-trust-700\" href=\"/contact\">Contact</a></nav><a class=\"hidden sm:inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-trust-500 px-5 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white transition hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:bg-trust-600\" href=\"/top-picks\">Shop Top Picks</a></div><nav class=\"lg:hidden border-t border-coral-100 bg-white\"><div class=\"no-scrollbar flex gap-2 overflow-x-auto px-4 py-2.5\"><a class=\"shrink-0 rounded-full border px-4 py-1.5 text-xs font-semibold transition border-coral-200 bg-cream-50 text-slate-700 hover:border-trust-400 hover:bg-trust-50 hover:text-trust-700\" href=\"/\">Home</a><a class=\"shrink-0 rounded-full border px-4 py-1.5 text-xs font-semibold transition border-coral-200 bg-cream-50 text-slate-700 hover:border-trust-400 hover:bg-trust-50 hover:text-trust-700\" href=\"/plushy-companions\">Plushy Companions</a><a class=\"shrink-0 rounded-full border px-4 py-1.5 text-xs font-semibold transition border-coral-200 bg-cream-50 text-slate-700 hover:border-trust-400 hover:bg-trust-50 hover:text-trust-700\" href=\"/ai-robotic-pets\">AI &amp; Robotic Pets</a><a class=\"shrink-0 rounded-full border px-4 py-1.5 text-xs font-semibold transition border-coral-200 bg-cream-50 text-slate-700 hover:border-trust-400 hover:bg-trust-50 hover:text-trust-700\" href=\"/best-for-seniors\">Seniors</a><a class=\"shrink-0 rounded-full border px-4 py-1.5 text-xs font-semibold transition border-coral-200 bg-cream-50 text-slate-700 hover:border-trust-400 hover:bg-trust-50 hover:text-trust-700\" href=\"/kids-and-families\">Kids &amp; Families</a><a class=\"shrink-0 rounded-full border px-4 py-1.5 text-xs font-semibold transition border-coral-200 bg-cream-50 text-slate-700 hover:border-trust-400 hover:bg-trust-50 hover:text-trust-700\" href=\"/best-for-gifts\">Gifts</a><a class=\"shrink-0 rounded-full border px-4 py-1.5 text-xs font-semibold transition border-coral-200 bg-cream-50 text-slate-700 hover:border-trust-400 hover:bg-trust-50 hover:text-trust-700\" href=\"/premium-picks\">Premium Picks</a><a class=\"shrink-0 rounded-full border px-4 py-1.5 text-xs font-semibold transition border-coral-200 bg-cream-50 text-slate-700 hover:border-trust-400 hover:bg-trust-50 hover:text-trust-700\" href=\"/compare\">Compare</a><a class=\"shrink-0 rounded-full border px-4 py-1.5 text-xs font-semibold transition border-coral-200 bg-cream-50 text-slate-700 hover:border-trust-400 hover:bg-trust-50 hover:text-trust-700\" href=\"/questions\">Questions?</a><a class=\"shrink-0 rounded-full border px-4 py-1.5 text-xs font-semibold transition border-coral-200 bg-cream-50 text-slate-700 hover:border-trust-400 hover:bg-trust-50 hover:text-trust-700\" href=\"/about\">About</a><a aria-current=\"page\" class=\"shrink-0 rounded-full border px-4 py-1.5 text-xs font-semibold transition border-trust-500 bg-trust-500 text-white\" href=\"/contact\">Contact</a></div></nav></header><main><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org/\",\"@type\":\"BreadcrumbList\",\"itemListElement\":[{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":1,\"name\":\"Home\",\"item\":\"https://interactivepetmarketplace.com/\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":2,\"name\":\"Contact\",\"item\":\"https://interactivepetmarketplace.com/contact\"}]}</script><section class=\"pt-14 pb-6 sm:pt-16 sm:pb-7 lg:pt-20 lg:pb-10\"><div class=\"container-shell\"><div class=\"max-w-3xl\"><p class=\"eyebrow\">Get in touch</p><h1 class=\"mt-3 text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-slate-900 sm:text-4xl\">Contact Interactive Pet Marketplace</h1><p class=\"mt-4 text-lg leading-8 text-slate-600\">Spotted an inaccurate price or feature? Have a suggestion, partnership idea, or a product we should review? We&#x27;d like to hear from you.</p></div></div></section><section class=\"pb-16 sm:pb-20\"><div class=\"container-shell\"><div class=\"grid gap-10 lg:grid-cols-[1.4fr_1fr]\"><div class=\"card p-6 sm:p-8\"><form class=\"space-y-5\" noValidate=\"\"><div><label for=\"name\" class=\"block text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900\">Name</label><input id=\"name\" type=\"text\" required=\"\" autoComplete=\"name\" class=\"mt-2 block w-full rounded-xl border border-coral-200 bg-white px-4 py-3 text-sm text-slate-900 placeholder:text-slate-400 focus:border-trust-500 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-trust-200\" name=\"name\"/></div><div><label for=\"email\" class=\"block text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900\">Email</label><input id=\"email\" type=\"email\" required=\"\" autoComplete=\"email\" class=\"mt-2 block w-full rounded-xl border border-coral-200 bg-white px-4 py-3 text-sm text-slate-900 placeholder:text-slate-400 focus:border-trust-500 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-trust-200\" name=\"email\"/></div><div><label for=\"topic\" class=\"block text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900\">What&#x27;s this about?</label><select id=\"topic\" name=\"topic\" required=\"\" class=\"mt-2 block w-full rounded-xl border border-coral-200 bg-white px-4 py-3 text-sm text-slate-900 focus:border-trust-500 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-trust-200\"><option value=\"\" disabled=\"\" selected=\"\">Choose a topic</option><option value=\"Product correction or update\">Product correction or update</option><option value=\"General feedback\">General feedback</option><option value=\"Press or partnership\">Press or partnership</option><option value=\"Other\">Other</option></select></div><div><label for=\"message\" class=\"block text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900\">Message</label><textarea id=\"message\" name=\"message\" required=\"\" rows=\"6\" class=\"mt-2 block w-full rounded-xl border border-coral-200 bg-white px-4 py-3 text-sm text-slate-900 placeholder:text-slate-400 focus:border-trust-500 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-trust-200\"></textarea></div><div aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"position:absolute;left:-9999px;width:1px;height:1px;overflow:hidden\"><label for=\"website\">Website (leave blank)</label><input id=\"website\" type=\"text\" tabindex=\"-1\" autoComplete=\"off\" name=\"website\"/></div><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-3 sm:flex-row sm:items-center sm:justify-between\"><p class=\"text-xs text-slate-500\">Your email is only used to reply to you. We don&#x27;t share it or add you to any list.</p><button type=\"submit\" class=\"btn-primary disabled:opacity-60 disabled:hover:translate-y-0\">Send message</button></div></form></div><aside class=\"space-y-6\"><div class=\"rounded-3xl border border-trust-200 bg-trust-50 p-6\"><h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-trust-900\">Response time</h3><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm leading-7 text-slate-700\">We read every message and aim to reply within a few business days. Complex questions or partnership discussions may take longer.</p></div><div class=\"rounded-3xl border border-coral-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-soft\"><h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900\">Helpful before you write</h3><ul class=\"mt-3 space-y-2 text-sm leading-7 text-slate-600\"><li>Looking for a particular product? Try the <a href=\"/compare\" class=\"underline text-trust-700 hover:text-trust-900\">compare page</a>.</li><li>Common questions are answered on the <a href=\"/questions\" class=\"underline text-trust-700 hover:text-trust-900\">questions page</a>.</li><li>For product corrections, please include the product name and what looks off — it speeds up our review.</li></ul></div><div class=\"rounded-3xl border border-coral-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-soft\"><h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900\">What we can&#x27;t help with</h3><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm leading-7 text-slate-600\">We&#x27;re not the manufacturer or seller of any product listed. For order status, returns, or warranty questions, please contact the retailer or manufacturer directly through their product page.</p></div></aside></div></div></section></main><footer class=\"border-t border-coral-200 bg-cream-100\"><div class=\"container-shell py-12\"><div class=\"grid gap-10 md:grid-cols-4\"><div class=\"md:col-span-2\"><p class=\"text-base font-semibold text-brand-900\">Interactive Pet Marketplace</p><p class=\"mt-3 max-w-sm text-sm leading-7 text-slate-600\">A cleaner way to compare companion-style plushy companions and AI &amp; robotic pets for seniors, families, and gift buyers.</p></div><div><p class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-brand-900\">Explore</p><div class=\"mt-4 space-y-3 text-sm text-slate-600\"><a class=\"block hover:text-brand-700\" href=\"/plushy-companions\">Plushy Companions</a><a class=\"block hover:text-brand-700\" href=\"/ai-robotic-pets\">AI &amp; Robotic Pets</a><a class=\"block hover:text-brand-700\" href=\"/best-for-seniors\">Seniors</a><a class=\"block hover:text-brand-700\" href=\"/compare\">Compare</a></div></div><div><p class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-brand-900\">About this site</p><div class=\"mt-4 space-y-3 text-sm text-slate-600\"><a class=\"block hover:text-brand-700\" href=\"/about\">About</a><a class=\"block hover:text-brand-700\" href=\"/contact\">Contact</a><a class=\"block hover:text-brand-700\" href=\"/about#affiliate-disclosure\">Affiliate disclosure</a></div></div></div><div class=\"mt-10 border-t border-coral-200 pt-6\"><p class=\"text-xs leading-6 text-slate-500\">Interactive Pet Marketplace may participate in affiliate programs and may earn a commission when you buy through links on this site, at no extra cost to you. See our <a class=\"underline hover:text-brand-700\" href=\"/about#affiliate-disclosure\">full affiliate disclosure</a> for details.</p></div></div></footer><!--$--><!--/$--><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/webpack-c8f26765e38997e7.js\" id=\"_R_\" async=\"\"></script><script>(self.__next_f=self.__next_f||[]).push([0])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"1:\\\"$Sreact.fragment\\\"\\n2:I[7121,[],\\\"\\\"]\\n3:I[4581,[],\\\"\\\"]\\n4:I[9504,[\\\"756\\\",\\\"static/chunks/756-98a13f2d10827e2b.js\\\",\\\"977\\\",\\\"static/chunks/app/contact/page-0da2a9740a533633.js\\\"],\\\"PageShell\\\"]\\n5:I[1526,[\\\"756\\\",\\\"static/chunks/756-98a13f2d10827e2b.js\\\",\\\"977\\\",\\\"static/chunks/app/contact/page-0da2a9740a533633.js\\\"],\\\"ContactForm\\\"]\\nb:I[7123,[],\\\"default\\\",1]\\n:HL[\\\"/_next/static/css/4dd59df00fa48bb6.css\\\",\\\"style\\\"]\\n\"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"0:{\\\"P\\\":null,\\\"c\\\":[\\\"\\\",\\\"contact\\\"],\\\"q\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"i\\\":false,\\\"f\\\":[[[\\\"\\\",{\\\"children\\\":[\\\"contact\\\",{\\\"children\\\":[\\\"__PAGE__\\\",{}]}]},\\\"$undefined\\\",\\\"$undefined\\\",16],[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$1\\\",\\\"c\\\",{\\\"children\\\":[[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"link\\\",\\\"0\\\",{\\\"rel\\\":\\\"stylesheet\\\",\\\"href\\\":\\\"/_next/static/css/4dd59df00fa48bb6.css\\\",\\\"precedence\\\":\\\"next\\\",\\\"crossOrigin\\\":\\\"$undefined\\\",\\\"nonce\\\":\\\"$undefined\\\"}]],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"html\\\",null,{\\\"lang\\\":\\\"en\\\",\\\"children\\\":[\\\"$\\\",\\\"body\\\",null,{\\\"children\\\":[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$L2\\\",null,{\\\"parallelRouterKey\\\":\\\"children\\\",\\\"error\\\":\\\"$undefined\\\",\\\"errorStyles\\\":\\\"$undefined\\\",\\\"errorScripts\\\":\\\"$undefined\\\",\\\"template\\\":[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$L3\\\",null,{}],\\\"templateStyles\\\":\\\"$undefined\\\",\\\"templateScripts\\\":\\\"$undefined\\\",\\\"notFound\\\":[[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"title\\\",null,{\\\"children\\